{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>MAiZE is a first person horror survival game set in a haunted corn maze. Navigate the maze to collect the five harvest items (an apple, an orange, a batch of grapes, a pear, and a cob of corn). Once all harvest items have been found, you can collect the Cornucopia to unlock the next section of the maze. Pumpkins scattered throughout the maze offer various buffs or debuffs. Evade the Scarecrows and other ghostly/demonic enemies that haunt the maze. Uncover the secrets of the maze and its haunted history.</i></strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398960/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736915181","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398960/page.bg.jpg?t=1736915181","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398960/5dde5e9a0ed9259eee92ec8ebda77c114e80595f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736915181","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398960/5dde5e9a0ed9259eee92ec8ebda77c114e80595f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736915181","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Various ghosts/ghouls, demons, and other variations of monsters that pursue and attack the player throughout the game. Jump scares and some monsters may be too scary for younger players. In later levels, player can fight back against certain enemies if they are able to collect the scythe weapon. Enemies that can be hurt by the scythe bleed and die from the attacks, or burst into flame."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>MAiZE is a first person horror survival game set in a haunted corn maze. Navigate the maze to collect the five harvest items (an apple, an orange, a batch of grapes, a pear, and a cob of corn). Once all harves